# System Prompts & Permanent Memory for Alina Hota Portfolio

## Aesthetic Memory
Strictly use the "Oryn" color palette:
- Deep charcoal/Black background: #050505
- Emerald Green primary: #10b981  
- High-contrast white text: #ffffff
- Neon glow effects on emerald elements
- Dark theme with cyber-noir aesthetic

## Constraint Memory
- Never use default "Hero" components or standard block templates
- Every section must match the layout proportions of the uploaded wireframes
- All animations must use Framer Motion AnimatePresence for smooth transitions
- Text transitions (specifically taglines) must use opacity and Y-axis shifts
- Profile picture must have thin, dashed circular border with orbital rotation animation

## Logic Memory
- All text transitions must use Framer Motion AnimatePresence for smooth opacity and Y-axis shifts
